        int commonDifference = sc.nextInt();

        System.out.println("Enter the value of n to find the nth term of the sequence: ");
        int n = sc.nextInt();

        int nthTerm = firstTerm + (n - 1) * commonDifference;
        System.out.println("The nth term of the arithmetic sequence is: " + nthTerm);
    }
}
```

